    "MissionGiver": "Citizens for Prosperity",
    "Title": "Get Supplies from Remote Outpost",
    "Description": "Hi,\n\nWe\u2019ve got a CFP team monitoring Headhunter activity at ~mission(Location|Address). They let me know a batch of recently stolen CFP supplies were moved into it. Since there\u2019s fewer defenses and personnel there, it feels like a good spot to strike and get our goods back. Interested?    \n\nDo this right and the bigger outpost won\u2019t know until it\u2019s too late. Get in, get the goods, and then bring them to ~mission(Destination|Address). Sound like a plan?\n\nAlso, to make your life easier, I'd make sure you have a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> with you. \n\nFly safe out there,\n\nLima Endicott\nLead Dispatcher\nCitizens for Prosperity",
